## LLM Wiki Maintenance
Every project has a wiki in .pi/memory/ maintained by you.
- index.md - catalog of all pages, keep updated.
- log.md - append-only log.
- pages/ - one per active topic.

Rules:
1. Update wiki after every meaningful change.
2. Keep index.md in sync.
3. Append to log.md with date and task.
Format: English only, plain text, no markdown formatting.